actions.message:
**Not following these rules will result in a mute/kick/ban depending on the severity of the violation!**
**1.** *No racism, discrimination, swearing or sexual content*
**2.** *No advertisment of any kind (GTA recoveries, other servers, ect.*
**3.** *Don't ask for a free service.*
**4.** *Do not ask when the next drop is, this will depend on when a staff member has time.*
**5.** *Be kind and respectful to each other.*
**6.** *Don't ask for the identity of a modder, they are just a middleman*
**7.** *We do not provide refunds, buying is at your own risk.*
**8.** *Asking for a free drop will be punished with a ban for the next public drop.*
**9.** *Do not DM staff, open a ticket if you have an issue.*
**10.** *Don't tag staff, this will result in a 30 minute mute and a warn* 
**11.** *Do not open a ticket without a valid reason, this will result in a 12 hour mute.*

**Rules can be changed at any time**

actions.message:
***__We will try to answer your Frequently Asked Questions here.__***


**Q:** *How often will you guys host a drop?*
**A:** *We try to host a drop everyday. But this will depend on the time off the droppers.*

**Q:** *How big is the change of getting banned?*
**A:** *So far, we have a 0% ban rate. So purchasing from us is save.*

**Q:** *What payment method do you accept?*
**A:** *We accept Paypal and IDEAL.*

**Q:** *How can I trust you with my account?*
**A:** *We screenshare everything we do in the time we are on your account, so you can see exactly what we are doing. You can also take a look in <#679057898151608322> for proof that we are trustworthy.*

**Q:** *Do you drop/mod on console?*
**A:** *No we don't profide modding on consoles, because you can't mod on any consolse. People who says that they can mod on console, will probably scam you.*
actions.name: Add Embed Field

actions.message:
**Q:** *How does a recovery work?*
**A:** *A recovery is a paid service where we log into your acount to deposit the money and levels you bought. We advise you to change you password before and afterwards, we also screenshare this whole process so you don't have to worry about your account getting stolen.*

**Still have a question? Feel free to ask it in <#700475403399331910>**
